headline: 2 Brilliant Stocks to Buy and Hold for 10 Years
summary: Let's consider two that could deliver solid returns through 2035: PayPal (NASDAQ: PYPL) and Airbnb (NASDAQ: ABNB).  A lot has changed for PayPal since 2014.  PayPal also revamped its management team last year.
